    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>General term for any tool or instrument having a handle surmounted by prongs, usually two to six in number, used for digging, lifting, or securing food, earth, or many other substances.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
